name: CNN
text: Researchers from MIT and Brigham and Women's Hospital in Boston have developed the iMASC, a new silicone mask that can be safely reused without fear of contamination. Researchers still need to analyze how effectively it catches viral particles https://t.co/zspXmkNYnc
